Detailed Description

c_des: Class IdentDlg. c_des: This class is used to show an identification dialog, which can be used to display a selected c_des: list which shows all selected structures, polygons, etc. in the drawing. When some elements become (de)selected, you'll have to click c_des: the Update button to get the actual information.
